          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": "Avast, matey! Ye 'ave stumbled upon our review o' a game that there be set amongst the 'igh seas. It be a tale o' naval combat, exploration an' shiny treasure booty. Ok, that's enough. With the recent House of Indies event held by Nintendo in leadup to Christmas, ",
            "type": "text",
            "version": 1
          },
          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 2,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": "Sail Forth",
            "type": "text",
            "version": 1
          },
          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": " was one of a few games that suddenly launched on the eShop the very same day. Being initially launched in an Indie World presentation back in 2021, ",
            "type": "text",
            "version": 1
          },
          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 2,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": "Sail Forth ",
            "type": "text",
            "version": 1
          },
          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": "has been a long time coming, so let's set sail together!",
            "type": "text",
            "version": 1
          }
        ],
        "direction": "ltr",
        "format": "",
        "indent": 0,
        "type": "paragraph",
        "version": 1
      },
      {
        "type": "embed",
        "url": "https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=cTXQiidpYDk",
        "html": "<iframe width=\"200\" height=\"113\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/cTXQiidpYDk?feature=oembed\" frameborder=\"0\" allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture\" allowfullscreen title=\"Sail Forth Launch Trailer | OUT NOW!\"></iframe>",
        "metadata": {
          "title": "Sail Forth Launch Trailer | OUT NOW!",
          "author_name": "The Quantum Astrophysicists Guild",
          "author_url": "https://www.youtube.com/@HypercubeGames",
